<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Following your recent insurance purchase, you opted to pay via monthly Direct Debit which is facilitated by Close Brothers Premium Finance. As part of </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Close Brothers’ Anti-Money Laundering checks</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, they are required to identify each of their customers.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Unfortunately </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">they have been unable to verify the ultimate beneficial owner(s) of the company and have asked if you could please complete the attached form and return it to us</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> so that they can proceed with their checks.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please contact us on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> if you have any further queries.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>